STATE
v.
WOGENSTAHL 1995-0042 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellant's motion for order or relief pursuant to S.C.Prac.R. 4.01. Motion denied.

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, Carr, Gallagher, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

French, J., concurs and would state that S.Ct.Prac.R. 4.01(A)(1) offers no basis for filing this motion.

Donna J. Carr, J., of the Ninth District Court of Appeals, sitting for Fischer, J.

Eileen T. Gallagher, J., of the Eighth District Court of Appeals, sitting for DeWine, J.
